{"tid":462871,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"多謝 idog 又一成就","createTime":"2017-11-09T03:15:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-09T04:07:29.000Z","uid":139716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e92cee1a5da3513ff07dad8f89eb42e77b00dbb6","tid":462871,"uid":139716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T03:15:53.000Z","msg":"蘋果股價再創新高　市值首破9000億美元<br />\n<br />\n全球市值最大的上市公司蘋果，股價在周三再創新高，成為首家市值突破9000億美元的企業。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果公司(Apple Inc., AAPL)週三股價上漲0.8%，創下176.24美元的歷史新高，市值達到9048.7億美元。<br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》指，蘋果是第一家市值突破9,000億美元的美國公司，今年5月已經成為首家市值達8,000億的美國公司。其市值只需要再增長11%，就將成為首家市值達1萬億美元的公司。根據截至10月20日的蘋果流通股數量，這意味著股價達到194.77美元。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果最新款iPhone上週上架。該科技巨頭最近公佈兩年來最強勁財政報告，受到所有主要產品銷售強勁和重要的中國市場出現反彈的支持，推動蘋果股價上漲。"},{"pid":"91b435a089f2270561173a5d405faaa87b6ce444","tid":462871,"uid":139716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T03:17:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://thestandnews.com/finance/%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E8%82%A1%E5%83%B9%E5%86%8D%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98-%E5%B8%82%E5%80%BC%E9%A6%96%E7%A0%B49000%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%25E8%2598%258B%25E6%259E%259C%25E8%2582%25A1%25E5%2583%25B9%25E5%2586%258D%25E5%2589%25B5%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%25AB%2598-%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%2580%25BC%25E9%25A6%2596%25E7%25A0%25B49000%25E5%2584%2584%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%2585%2583%2F&d=Ye4xvbTKLIGs6GZxb87OX3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=e629b6a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%25E8%2598%258B%25E6%259E%259C%25E8%2582%25A1%25E5%2583%25B9%25E5%2586%258D%25E5%2589%25B5%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%25AB%2598-%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%2580%25BC%25E9%25A6%2596%25E7%25A0%25B49000%25E5%2584%2584%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%2585%2583%2F&h=acc06bda\" target=\"_blank\">http://thestandnews.com/finance/%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E8%82%A1%E5%83%B9%E5%86%8D%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98-%E5%B8%82%E5%80%BC%E9%A6%96%E7%A0%B49000%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5